prompts.prompt: 1. Initialize state variables for a TypeScript/React to-do app with gamification features. These include an array to store tasks (taskArray) and an object to store user information (userInfo) which includes points and level.

2. Structure the task object for a TypeScript/React to-do app with gamification features. The task object should include the following attributes: title, description, due date, status, an array of subtasks (subtaskArray), and points.
